- First SSO login succeeds (no errors)
- User is redirected to webapp dashboard
- Dashboard is accessible (proves account was created)
- User menu displays correct email/name
- Session persists across reload
- Second login works normally (user now exists in Grid DB)
- Test implicitly proves /auth/sso/callback JIT provisioning logic works

